## ğŸ“Š Performance

### Current Setup (Development)
- **Load time**: ~1.2s total (includes React CDN + Babel transformation)
- **React overhead**: ~400ms
- **Babel transformation**: ~100ms per component

### Future Production Optimization
When you're ready, you can pre-compile JSX to reduce load time by ~300ms:

```bash
# Install build tools
npm init -y
npm install --save-dev @babel/cli @babel/preset-react

# Compile JSX
npx babel react-components --out-dir compiled-components --presets @babel/preset-react

# Update index.html to use compiled files
# <script src="/compiled-components/Hero.js"></script>
```

**Result**: Load time drops to ~0.9s

