## ğŸ”’ Security Notes

### Current Setup
- React loaded from unpkg.com CDN (integrity check recommended)
- Babel Standalone runs in browser (development only)
- No security changes to Django backend
- All existing CORS and CSP policies remain

### Production Recommendations

1. **Use integrity hashes for CDN scripts**
   ```html
   <script
     crossorigin
     src="https://unpkg.com/react@18/umd/react.production.min.js"
     integrity="sha384-..."
   ></script>
   ```

2. **Pre-compile JSX** (remove Babel Standalone)

3. **Add to CSP** (if you have Content-Security-Policy)
   ```
   script-src 'self' https://unpkg.com
   ```

